ZH: 人们听到有新货到了，便蜂拥而来。
EN: When people hear new stock has arrived, they flock to it.

ZH: 一打折的商品，顾客便蜂拥而来。
EN: Customers flock to products on sale.

ZH: 远足季节到来，游客们蜂拥而来。
EN: The hiking season has arrived, and tourists flock in.

ZH: 媒体报道流行的餐馆，食客们蜂拥而来。
EN: When the media reports about popular restaurants, diners flock in.

ZH: 商场开业时，人们蜂拥而来购物。
EN: People flock to the mall for shopping when it opens.

ZH: 这家商店举办折扣促销活动，顾客们蜂拥而来。
EN: This store holds a discount promotion, and customers flock in.

ZH: 开幕式开始后，观众们蜂拥而来占座位。
EN: After the opening ceremony begins, the audience rushes in to grab seats.

ZH: 新秀艺人的演出，粉丝们蜂拥而来支持他们。
EN: Fans flock to support the performances of new talented artists.

ZH: 雨后光天化日，人们蜂拥而来晒太阳。
EN: People flock to sunbathe on a clear day after rain.

ZH: 著名艺术家的画展，观众们蜂拥而来欣赏艺术作品。
EN: Audiences flock to appreciate the artwork at the famous artist's exhibition.

ZH: 餐馆升级装修后，食客们蜂拥而来体验新的氛围。
EN: Diners rush to experience the new ambiance after the restaurant's renovation.

ZH: 精彩的音乐会票一开售，乐迷们便蜂拥而来购买。
EN: When tickets for an exciting concert go on sale, music lovers flock to buy them.

ZH: 假期期间，游客们蜂拥而来参观名胜古迹。
EN: Tourists flock to visit famous landmarks during the holidays.

ZH: 新餐厅开业，美食爱好者们蜂拥而来品尝美味佳肴。
EN: Food enthusiasts rush to the new restaurant to taste delicious dishes.

ZH: 在夜市上，人们蜂拥而来购买各种小吃。
EN: People flock to the night market to buy various snacks.

ZH: 偶像歌手开唱，他的粉丝们蜂拥而来聆听他的音乐。
EN: Idol singers' fans flock to listen to their music performances.

ZH: 天黑了，人们蜂拥而来欣赏烟花表演。
EN: As soon as it gets dark, people flock to enjoy the fireworks show.

ZH: 电影院上映了一部热门电影，观众们蜂拥而来观看。
EN: A popular movie is released in the cinema, and audiences flock to watch it.

ZH: 深夜烤肉店营业期间，夜猫子们蜂拥而来品尝烤肉。
EN: During late-night hours at the BBQ restaurant, night owls flock to taste grilled meat.

ZH: 过年期间，人们会蜂拥而来拜访亲戚朋友。
EN: During the Chinese New Year, people flock to visit relatives and friends.
